nodes.text: The Rana'Inrull District was a district in the Duros Sector of the moon Nar Shaddaa during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire. The district was home to Duros Plaza and Mutotech Labs.
The Rana'Inrull District appears as part of the Duros Sector in Star Wars: The Old Republic, a video game released by BioWare in 2011.
